<p>Roberts recently joined DailyMailTV as the new host for season four which officially kicks off September 14th. </p>

<p>One of Jenn's first interviews of the new season of Extra was with singer Brandy about her epic Verzuz battle with Monica.</p>

<p>The singer said she was 'so blessed' to have raised a quarter of a million dollars as part of it for the vote campaign.</p>

